OL,3,CFire station demolition on hold as new
OL,4,Ccouncil debate ordered amid Gormley row
OL,6,FThe future of Hexham's former fire
OL,7,Fstation remains up in the air, amid a
OL,8,Frow over whether it should be sold to
OL,9,FSir Antony Gormley.
OL,11,FNorthumberland County Council's
OL,12,Fleadership decided last month to
OL,13,Fdemolish the disused building in order
OL,14,Fto make way for the development of an
OL,15,Fexpanded Tyne Mills council depot.
