OL,6,FBut that move, which has sparked a
OL,7,Fpublic outcry from locals keen to see
OL,8,Fthe space taken over by the acclaimed
OL,9,Fsculptor, will stay on hold for now as
OL,10,Fthe battle appears set to rumble on
OL,11,Fahead of a new public debate, the
OL,12,FLocal Democracy Reporting Service
OL,13,Freports.
