OL,3,CFire station demolition on hold as new
OL,4,Ccouncil debate ordered amid Gormley row
OL,6,FMore than 3,000 people have signed a
OL,7,Fpetition calling on the council to
OL,8,Fsell and hundreds of Hexham residents
OL,9,Frecently staged a protest in support
OL,10,Fof the artist's ambition to turn the
OL,11,Fold fire station into a storage and
OL,12,Fexhibition space, gathering at Sele
OL,13,FHill to form a human Angel of the
OL,14,FNorth in homage to his most famous
OL,15,Fwork.
