OL,3,CFire station demolition on hold as new
OL,4,Ccouncil debate ordered amid Gormley row
OL,6,FFollowing the Conservative cabinet's
OL,7,FNovember decision not to sell the site
OL,8,Fto Sir Antony, the matter was 'called
OL,9,Fin' by opposition councillors for a
OL,10,Fspecial scrutiny meeting held on
OL,11,FWednesday afternoon (3 December).
OL,13,FAt that hearing, it was determined
OL,14,Fthat the issue would be sent to be
OL,15,Fdebated at a full council meeting
OL,16,Fbefore the demolition works can
OL,17,Fproceed.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/11
