OL,6,FHowever, while the decision remains
OL,7,Fpaused and the full council can order
OL,8,Fthe cabinet to reconsider, the final
OL,9,Fverdict will ultimately rest with the
OL,10,Fcabinet.
OL,12,FHexham mayor Derek Kennedy, who leads
OL,13,Fthe council's independent group, led
OL,14,Fthe call-in move and claimed that
OL,15,Fthere had not been proper
OL,16,Fconsideration given to alternative
OL,17,Foptions.
