OL,6,FHe suggested that a Gormley attraction
OL,7,Fcould be worth #3 million per year to
OL,8,Fthe market town and that a "split
OL,9,Fsite" to accommodate both Sir Antony's
OL,10,Fplans and the council's needs should
OL,11,Fbe explored.
OL,13,FLib Dem Suzanne Fairless Aitken
OL,14,Faccused the local authority of
OL,15,F"glaring failures as well as
OL,16,Fmisinformation", while Labour's Scott
OL,17,FDickinson said that the decision had
OL,18,Fcome about in "a way that seems
OL,19,Fdeceitful".
