OL,3,CFire station demolition on hold as new
OL,4,Ccouncil debate ordered amid Gormley row
OL,6,FStephen Gerrard, the council's
OL,7,Fmonitoring officer, said that the
OL,8,Fproper procedure to take the decision
OL,9,Fas an urgent item had been followed.
OL,11,FNick Oliver, the Tory cabinet's member
OL,12,Ffor finance, said suggestions that
OL,13,Flocal councillors were shocked by the
OL,14,Fdemolition proposals were "completely
OL,15,Funfathomable".
OL,17,FHe reiterated that the fire station
OL,18,Fhad never been for sale and said the
OL,19,Fcouncil had previously rejected
OL,20,Fapproaches to turn it into a cycling
OL,21,Fhub or a climbing centre.
