OL,3,CFire station demolition on hold as new
OL,4,Ccouncil debate ordered amid Gormley row
OL,6,FCllr Oliver said that there was a need
OL,7,Fto expand the depot facility and
OL,8,Fprovide extra space for vehicle
OL,9,Fmaintenance and MOT testing, adding:
OL,10,F"There was no secret plot to try and
OL,11,Fhide it (the cabinet decision) from
OL,12,Fthe public or Hexham Town Council or
OL,13,Fanyone else. We were just trying to
OL,14,Fget the information out there as
OL,15,Fopenly and quickly as possible."
