OL,3,CFire station demolition on hold as new
OL,4,Ccouncil debate ordered amid Gormley row
OL,6,FAfter a proposal from Tory councillor
OL,7,FJohn Beynon to allow the decision to
OL,8,Fproceed was voted down, a majority of
OL,9,Fscrutiny committee members instead
OL,10,Fbacked a move to refer it to full
OL,11,Fcouncil.
OL,13,FLabour councillor Elizabeth Dunn said
OL,14,Fresidents "deserve" to hear the issue
OL,15,Fdebated, while Reform's Trevor Austin
OL,16,Fadded: "I think we should discuss it
OL,17,Fat full council, put the thing to bed
OL,18,Fand make a proper decision ` with
OL,19,Fhopefully a more united council."
